"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-jess-learmonth-pregnancy-triathlon-paris-2024-b2495314.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Learmonth, who won gold in the triathlon mixed relay at Tokyo 2020, became a mum for the first time when giving birth to Frederick last September  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9486391142192899, \"rank\": 0.05414116797636187, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.690326267646597e-18, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Olympicschampion Jess Learmonth says she pushed the boundaries during her unexpected pregnancy in a bid to keep herParis 2024dream alive.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jess Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth, who won gold in thetriathlonmixed relay at Tokyo 2020, became a mum for the first time when giving birth to Frederick last September.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9486391142192899, \"rank\": 0.05414116797636187, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old from Leeds fell pregnant during her recovery from a serious hip injury and, having not competed since May 2022, is on a mission to get back to her best in time for this summer's Olympics.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"score\": 0.9947993241806455, \"rank\": 0.005185650264359694, \"text\": \"Leeds\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told the PA news agency: \\\"I probably should not have run on the day I gave birth.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I actually pulled my calf on a run in the morning and then gave birth that evening.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, I was heavily over my usual running weight and obviously my gait was completely different because I had a big belly.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe if I had not pulled my calf I'd have said it was fine.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, looking back, with two weeks to go, I probably could have just chilled out a little bit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth, determined to hit the ground running once Frederick was born, found medical research into training while pregnant to be limited.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.690326267646597e-18, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until the turn of the century, it was rare to see women return to the top of their sport after giving birth.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth is grateful to the doctors and sports scientists at the National Sports Centre at Bisham Abbey and British Triathlon for their support.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\", \"score\": 0.582006492548568, \"rank\": 0.718193879668866, \"text\": \"National Sports Centre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were certain things I obviously did follow,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The massive one is not running for 12 weeks post-birth.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you come back too early, you can have problems later down the line.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I followed all the advice, but it was the stuff they were not sure on that I kind of explored myself.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was still lifting heavy weights in the gym.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I took the information and filtered it for me.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They helped me find my own boundaries and explore what I could and could not manage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth stressed that throughout her pregnancy she never allowed her heart rate to go beyond 150 beats per minute, while her approach, so far, appears to be paying off.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Running aside, she is closing in on the performance levels that saw her win Olympic gold and finish second overall in the 2019 World Series after multiple podium finishes.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not far away,\\\" said the 2017 European champion.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999996392508106, \"rank\": 3.0812784402671664e-07, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just not as good as I was before, yet.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been big changes in my life, having Fred and not training as much.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's\\u00a0interesting to see how my body will react to doing less training and more recovery.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could go either way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth has been surprised by her progress as she targets the first Indoor World Cup event of the season in Lievin, France, for her return to competitive action at the end of March.\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 3071, \"end\": 3077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e9vin\", \"score\": 0.9944831484053038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lievin\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e9vin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e9vin\"}, {\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.965968997935491, \"rank\": 0.03483667484958087, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Frederick's helped me a lot because we have done a lot of tests in the lab and my numbers are probably just as good, if not better, than pre-pregnancy, certainly on the bike, which has kind of baffled me really,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.690326267646597e-18, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know if having him and the different hormones you get from having a child and post-birth has kind of helped me out, but it's been really, really motivating.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But after pregnancy, I have found it a lot harder than I thought I would, mainly because of the logistics of him feeding and napping.\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am breastfeeding as well, so it's difficult to get the timing right.\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to make sure, logistically, I am on it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth, made an MBE in 2022, will not be the first triathlete to return to top-level action after giving birth as fellow Brit and former world champion Vicky Holland and Americans Katie Zaferes and Gwen Jorgensen have paved the way.\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 4037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 3821, \"end\": 3824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6252692399596606e-14, \"text\": \"MBE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\"}, {\"begin\": 3957, \"end\": 3970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicky Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\"}, {\"begin\": 3985, \"end\": 3998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Zaferes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Zaferes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Zaferes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Zaferes\"}, {\"begin\": 4003, \"end\": 4017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwen_Jorgensen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gwen Jorgensen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwen_Jorgensen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwen_Jorgensen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have definitely inspired me,\\\" Learmonth added.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4075, \"end\": 4084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wish there was more definitive research out there that shows athletes can have children and come back and be just as good.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is still a lot of stigma around training through pregnancy and certainly what I was doing and I'd love to help get more exposure and help inspire all new mums who want to get back into sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4476, \"end\": 4487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.417761832567054e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"